title: Barney Miller 1975-1982 (Complete TV series in MP4 format)
description:
"Barney Miller" is a sitcom set in a New York City police station. The show aired from 1975 to 1982. Each episode is in this complete collection is in MP4 format. 

Characters: Cptn. Barney Miller, Sgt. Fish, Sgt. Wojo, Sgt. Harris, Sgt. Yemana, Sgt. Amanguale, Sgt. Dietrich, Inspector Luger, Officer Levitt
